handy/handy dog
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:a cross between a hunting, heading and perhaps a backing dog in its functions.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See: shandygaff
